Given the following program and the specified variable, optimize it out by constant propagation or copy propagation. If this variable is unused, just optimize it out.. The program is 
struct h {
  long i;
  int j;
  long k;
};
static struct h fn1(struct h p) {
  while (1)
    p.k;
}
unsigned fn2() {
  struct h p;
  fn1(p);
  while (1) {
    struct h r;
    p = r = p;
  }
}
int main() {}
.                 The target to be optimized is `k` (global variable).
